src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6732bf0cb839be75ac6e092e96ae5ab6b760d59d","tid":1953722,"uid":254376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab8a9b0f929d2392d4034c970f3ff2841ee2505b","tid":1953722,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:56:57.000Z","msg":"一定唔會有人後悔同傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都好想自殺，反正係一個邊緣人+活死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"做咩想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c2d88a91023304569de50f9c30fa6a6551dfa8","tid":1953722,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"死左會去狗屋揾替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f893b1fbd040e4be3654adb930d570da9583bfb3","tid":1953722,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab8a9b0f929d2392d4034c970f3ff2841ee2505b","tid":1953722,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:56:57.000Z","msg":"一定唔會有人後悔同傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都好想自殺，反正係一個邊緣人+活死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:19:35.000Z","msg":"看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=17657e8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=5b363b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a> ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}